general.headline: Solicitor at Smythe Wozniak Lawyers
general.description:
While working within legal industry since 2004, Ellen is a disciplined and passionate lawyer who strives to achieve the best outcomes for her clients. She enjoys the interaction with clients and her attention to detail ensures that every matter achieves a timely and accurate outcome with a minimum of stress. Ellen has practiced in the following areas of law including Property Law, Wills, Probate/Estate matters, Criminal Law, Family Law, Dispute Resolution & Litigation and Commercial Law. 

Ellen is admitted in both the Supreme Court of NSW and High Court of Australia, and is a current member of the Law Society of NSW. 

Please do not hesitate to contact Ellen if you require any assistance.
